title: Baked Chop Suey
ingredients: ["1 lb. ground beef", "1 small onion, chopped", "1 c. celery, chopped", "1 (10 1/2 oz.) can cream of chicken soup", "1 (10 1/2 oz.) can cream of mushroom soup", "1 1/2 c. warm water", "1/4 c. soy sauce", "salt and pepper to taste", "1 can Chinese noodles"]
directions: ["Brown the meat with the onion.", "Mix together all ingredients except the noodles.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 1 hour.", "Add noodles.", "Mix 3/4 into the casserole and spread the rest evenly over the top. Bake 15 minutes longer."]
NER: ["cream of chicken soup", "soy sauce", "cream of mushroom soup", "onion", "water", "celery", "chinese noodles", "ground beef", "salt"]

title: Chicken Picante
ingredients: ["1/2 c. medium hot chunky taco sauce", "1/4 c. Dijon mustard", "2 Tbsp. lime juice", "6 boneless, skinned chicken breasts", "2 Tbsp. butter", "6 Tbsp. sour cream", "1 lime, sliced"]
directions: ["In large bowl, combine taco sauce, mustard and lime juice; mix well.", "Add chicken, turning to coat; marinate for 30 minutes.", "In large heavy skillet, melt butter until foamy.", "Remove chicken from marinade; fry until browned on all sides, turning frequently.", "Add remaining marinade; cook about 5 minutes longer, until chicken is fork-tender.", "Remove chicken, boil marinade 1 minute and spoon over chicken.", "Place 1 tablespoon sour cream on top of each piece; top with lime segment."]

title: Baked Potato Soup
ingredients: ["2/3 c. butter", "2/3 c. flour", "7 c. milk", "4 large potatoes, baked, cooled, peeled and cubed (about 4 c.)", "4 green onions, sliced", "12 bacon strips, cooked and crumbled", "1 1/4 c. shredded Cheddar cheese", "1 c. sour cream", "3/4 tsp. salt", "1/2 tsp. pepper"]
directions: ["In a large soup kettle, melt the butter.", "Stir in flour; heat and stir until smooth.", "Gradually add milk, stirring constantly, until thickened.", "Add potatoes and onions.", "Bring to a boil, stirring constantly.", "Reduce heat; simmer for 10 minutes.", "Add remaining ingredients; stir until cheese is melted.", "Serve immediately."]

title: Chunky Chocolate Chip Brownie-Type Cookies
ingredients: ["3 c. self-rising flour", "2 c. chocolate chips", "1 1/2 Tbsp. vanilla", "1 1/2 c. brown sugar", "2 c. granulated sugar", "3 eggs", "1 1/2 c. Crisco shortening"]
directions: ["Preheat oven to 375\u00b0.", "Cream shortening, sugars, eggs and vanilla together.", "Blend in chocolate chips.", "Gradually add in flour on medium speed of mixer.", "Bake for 30 to 35 minutes.", "Cool for 25 minutes, then cut into squares."]

title: Pumpkin Bread
ingredients: ["3 c. granulated sugar", "3 1/2 c. flour", "2 tsp. soda", "1 tsp. salt", "1 tsp. nutmeg", "1 tsp. cinnamon", "1 Tbsp. pumpkin pie spice", "4 eggs", "2/3 c. water", "2 c. pumpkin"]
directions: ["In large bowl, mix first seven ingredients.", "Add eggs, water and pumpkin.", "Beat thoroughly.", "Pour into 1 pound coffee cans, filling cans about halfway.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for one hour."]
